profile:
Landscape Design and Garden Company located in NIAGARA FALLS, ONTARIO.

Our core service is renovating and installing complete new gardens. 

Our gardens include a variety of annuals, perennials, shrubs and trees. 

We also install into our gardens:
- Stone work (retaining walls, stepping stones, patio slabs, armour stone, decorative stone, sculpture)
- New turf and lawn. Synthetic or real grass. Need a small putting green, or do you have a space where no grass grows. We install. 
- Decks and Fences
- Landscape lighting
- Irrigation systems 
- Ponds & Water Features
